  "title": "H2 behaves ideally",
  "content": {
    "prompt": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following best explains why <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H 2, gas\"><math alttext=\"H 2, gas\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><msub><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></math></span></span> behaves more ideally than most other gases?</p>\n",
    "answer": "i4",
    "choices": [
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The number of particles in a given volume of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H 2, gas\"><math alttext=\"H 2, gas\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>g</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is smallest in comparison to other gases, because the molar mass of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H 2\"><math alttext=\"H 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is smallest.</p>",
        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Collisions between gas particles and the walls of a container are more frequent for smaller molecules, because the average velocity is very high.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The average kinetic energy of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H 2\"><math alttext=\"H 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> molecules at a given temperature is large, because the average velocity of the <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H 2\"><math alttext=\"H 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> molecules is very high.</p>",
        "value": "i3"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">Intermolecular attractions between <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H 2\"><math alttext=\"H 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><msub><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow></mstyle></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> molecules are weak, because the electron clouds of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"H 2\"><math alttext=\"H 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mrow><msub><mrow><mtext>H</mtext></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msub></mrow></math></span></span> molecules are small.</p>",
        "value": "i4"
      }
    ]
